<!-- table class (.table):- this class adds basic styling to the table. -->
<!-- striped Row class (.table-striped):- this class adds zebra-striping to any table row within the table. It makes it easier to read rows of data by providing a contrasting background color for every other row. -->
<!-- bordered Table class (.table-bordered):- this class adds borders on all sides of the table and cells. -->
<!-- hover row class (.table-hover):- this class adds a hover effect on table rows. When you hover over a row, it will change the background color to indicate that the row is active or selected. -->
<!-- dark Table class (.table-dark):- this class adds a dark background color to the table and its cells. -->
<!-- borderless Table class (.table-borderless):- this class removes borders from the table and its cells. -->
